\c 4
\s Pauro unoparidza Jesu Kristu nemoyo wose
\p
\v 1 Naizvozvo zvatine kushumira uku, sezvatakagamuchira ngoni, hatineti;
\v 2 asi takarasha zvinhu zvakavanzika zvinonyadza, tisingafambi neusvatu, kana kushandisa shoko raMwari nekunyengera; asi nekuratidza chokwadi, tichizvipupurira kuhana dzevanhu vose pamberi paMwari.
\v 3 Zvino kana evhangeri yedu yakafukidzwa, yakafukidzwa kune avo vanoparara;
\v 4 kwavari Mwari wenyika ino wavakapofumadza fungwa dzevasingatendi, zvimwe chiedza chekubwinya kweevhangeri yaKristu uri mufananidzo waMwari chingavhenekera kwavari.
\v 5 Nekuti hatizviparidzi isu, asi Kristu Jesu Ishe; uye isu \add tiri\add* varanda venyu nekuda kwaJesu.
\v 6 Nekuti Mwari wakati chiedza chivhenekere parima ndiye wakavhenekera mumoyo yedu, kuti \add atipe\add* chiedza cheruzivo rwokubwinya kwaMwari pachiso chaJesu Kristu.
\v 7 Asi tine fuma iyi mumidziyo yevhu, kuti ukuru hwesimba hwuve hwaMwari, uye hwusabva kwatiri;
\v 8 \add tino\add*tambudzwa pamativi ose, asi ha\add ti\add*manikidzwi; \add tino\add*kanganiswa, asi hatiori moyo;
\v 9 \add tino\add*tambudzwa, asi kwete kusiyiwa; \add tino\add*wisirwa pasi, asi kwete kuparadzwa;
\v 10 tichitakura nguva dzose kufa kwaIshe Jesu mumuviri, kuti neupenyuwo hwaJesu hwuratidzwe mumuviri wedu.
\v 11 Nekuti isu vapenyu tinogara tichikumikidzwa mukufa nekuda kwaJesu, kuti upenyuwo hwaJesu hwuratidzwe munyama yedu inofa.
\v 12 Saizvozvo kufa kunobata matiri, asi upenyu mamuri.
\v 13 Naizvozvo tine mweya iwoyu werutendo, zvichienderana nezvazvakanyorwa \add zvichinzi\add*: Ndakatenda, saka naizvozvo ndakataura; isuwo tinotenda saka naizvozvo tinotaura;
\v 14 tichiziva kuti iye wakamutsa Ishe Jesu, uchatimutsawo isu kubudikidza naJesu; agotikumikidza pamwe nemwi.
\v 15 Nekuti zvinhu zvose \add zvinoitwa\add* nekuda kwenyu, kuti nyasha zvadzakawanzwa nekuda kwekuvonga kwevazhinji dziwedzerwe dzive rukudzo kuna Mwari.
\s Kutambudzika kwepano panyika ndekwenguva duku
\p
\v 16 Naizvozvo hatineti, asi kunyange munhu wedu wokunze achiparara, zvakadaro womukati unovandudzwa zuva rimwe nerimwe.
\v 17 Nekuti kutambudzika kwedu kwakareruka kuripo asi kwechinguva chiduku, kunotiitira kubwinya kukuru kwakaisvo-naka kusina chiyero;
\v 18 Nekuti tisingatariri zvinhu zvinoonekwa, asi zvinhu zvisingaonekwi; nekuti zvinhu zvinoonekwa ndezvenguva, asi zvinhu zvisingaonekwi \add ndezve\add*kusingaperi.
